m\",\"children\":\"Are the resumes ATS-friendly?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. All four templates use real text (not images), standard fonts, and a clean heading hierarchy that Applicant Tracking Systems can parse correctly.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Do I need to create an account?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Do I need to create an account?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"No. You can start building your resume immediately without signing up or providing any personal information.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Is my data private and secure?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Is my data private and secure?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Your resume data never leaves your browser. All processing happens client-side on your device, so your personal and professional information stays completely private.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I download my resume as a PDF?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I download my resume as a PDF?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes — click 'Download PDF' and get an instant, high-quality PDF with no watermarks and no paywall. Unlike Resume.io and Zety, the download is truly free.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I save multiple resumes?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I save multiple resumes?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Save resumes to your local history, name them, and switch between versions. You can also export all resumes as JSON for backup and import them later.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What sections can I add to my resume?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"What sections can I add to my resume?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"11 section types are available: Professional Summary, Work Experience, Education, Skills, Certifications, Languages, Projects, Volunteer Experience, Awards & Honors, Publications, and References. You can add, remove, reorder, and show/hide any section.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I customize the look of my resume?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I customize the look of my resume?\"}],\"$L39\"]}],\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\"]}]]}]\n31:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Two-column layouts that break ATS parsing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Many \\\"pretty\\\" resume templates use sidebars or columns that ATS systems read out of order. The included templates use single-column flows on purpose — they look modern without breaking parsing.\"}]]}]\n32:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Listing every skill you've ever touched\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2c:1:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shr