\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Is this resume builder really free?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported so it can remain free for everyone.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Are the resumes ATS-friendly?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Are the resumes ATS-friendly?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. All four templates use real text (not images), standard fonts, and a clean heading hierarchy that Applicant Tracking Systems can parse correctly.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Do I need to create an account?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Do I need to create an account?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"No. You can start building your resume immediately without signing up or providing any personal information.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Is my data private and secure?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Is my data private and secure?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Your resume data never leaves your browser. All processing happens client-side on your device, so your personal and professional information stays completely private.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I download my resume as a PDF?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-m