 on your device, so your personal and professional information stays completely private.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I download my resume as a PDF?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I download my resume as a PDF?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes — click 'Download PDF' and get an instant, high-quality PDF with no watermarks and no paywall. Unlike Resume.io and Zety, the download is truly free.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I save multiple resumes?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I save multiple resumes?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Save resumes to your local history, name them, and switch between versions. You can also export all resumes as JSON for backup and import them later.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What sections can I add to my resume?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"What sections can I add to my resume?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"11 section types are available: Professional Summary, Work Experience, Education, Skills, Certifications, Languages, Projects, Volunteer Experience, Awards & Honors, Publications, and References. You can add, remove, reorder, and show/hide any section.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I customize the look of my resume?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium\",\"children\":\"Can I customize the look of my resume?\"}],\"$L22